<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Agamemnon" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Agamemnon,</orth> the leader of the Greeks before Troy: <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.4.237" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 4, 237</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.6" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 6, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.2.148" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 2, 148</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 1.2.267" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 2, 267</bibl> (and often).
